headline: MYR Group (MYRG) Tops Q2 Earnings and Revenue Estimates
summary: MYR (MYRG) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of +8.97% and +8.74%, respectively, for the quarter ended June 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
